OL,3,CMerseyrail strikes called off after
OL,4,Cimproved pay offer
OL,6,FA planned three-day strike by workers
OL,7,Fon Merseyrail has been called off
OL,8,Fafter an improved pay offer was made.
OL,10,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,11,FTransport union (RMT) were due to walk
OL,12,Fout from Saturday 18 July.
OL,14,FThe union said it will now consider
OL,15,Fthe offer.
