OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784465300
OL,3,CMerseyrail strikes called off after
OL,4,Cimproved pay offer
OL,6,FNeil Grabham, managing director of
OL,7,FMerseyrail, said: "We are pleased that
OL,8,Fthe RMT has agreed to postpone the
OL,9,Fplanned industrial action while its
OL,10,Fmembers consider and vote on the
OL,11,Fimproved offer that has been put
OL,12,Fforward.
OL,14,F"This is positive news for our
OL,15,Fcustomers, our employees and the
OL,16,FLiverpool City Region.
OL,26,@oD@SOUvD@AOU
